Author: tcs_hearts
Text: Right. Like I don't understand the phrase "I wouldn't want to be that thin." It's totally wild to me that people don't want to be as skinny as possible.

Author: annielovesbacon
Text: I always forget that non-disordered people aren’t obsessive about their calories and actually *want* to be a healthy weight. I’ve had an ed so long I just completely forget that it’s abnormal.
